{center}
{subhead}Hyperion Entertainment Announcement{def}
{left}
{pp}
18.2.2003
{pp}
SciTech Software Inc. and Hyperion Entertainment VOF are pleased to announce they have
enterered into a strategic partnership which will see SciTech's SNAP(tm) technology
integrated into AmigaOS 4.x which is currently under development by Hyperion for PPC
based systems.
{pp}
SciTech SNAP, SciTech's leading edge graphics device support, allows for the rapid
development and deployment of embedded solutions across multiple platforms and currently
already supports well over 170 different graphics chipsets including all the latest
offerings from industry leaders ATI, nVidia and Matrox.
{pp}
A full list of supported chipsets can be found here. Read more
{pp}